# MotionPitch — Core Rules

## Hard constraints

- **Package manager:** `bun` only. Never `npm`, `yarn`, `pnpm`.
- **Framework:** Next.js 15, App Router only.
- **LLM output:** Always structured JSON. **Never** request raw SVG from the model.
- **Hand-crafted templates are the moat.** Don't generate or modify SVG templates with the LLM.

## Workflow

- Read the directory's `AGENTS.md` before editing files in it.
- Prefer editing existing files over creating new ones.
- After substantive edits: `bun run lint && bun run typecheck`.
- Commit messages: [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/).

## Out of scope (do not build)

Auth, persistence, databases, post-generation editing, multi-page output, image generation, > 4 templates, mobile-specific layouts.

If asked to build any of these, redirect to `docs/demo-script.md`.
